quran[56]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,"Ewe Owifumbesiye mutsingubo."
  74,2,"Bukha mana wikanyilisie!"
  74,3,"Ne witsoomie Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi."
  74,4,"Ne olafie tsingubo tsitsio."
  74,5,"Ne owuuye keshifwolo."
  74,6,"Ne olarusia nosuubile okhwenya eshinji tawe."
  74,7,"Ne wisumilisie khulwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi."
  74,8,"Mana olwa olwika lulifurwamwo."
  74,9,"Kho inyanga eyo iliba inyanga indinyu muno."
  74,10,"Khubakhayi shiiliba inyangu tawe."
  74,11,"Ndekha nende wandaloonga sienyene."
  74,12,"Mana nemuhelesia emiandu eminji."
  74,13,"Nende abaana balolekha."
  74,14,"Ne nemukasilia amakhuwa obulayi muno."
  74,15,"Mana khandi yekombanga mbu emumeete."
  74,16,"Shikali kario tawe! Toto ye yakholelanga eshileka muno amakhuwa kefu (Ikurani)."
  74,17,"Nditsa okhumuha eshinyasio shialanyala okhwisumilisia tawe."
  74,18,"Toto ye yapara mana napanga shinga atuta."
  74,19,"Mana nasishibwa okhurulana shingala yapanga okhututa."
  74,20,"Khandi mana nasishibwa okhurulana shingala yapanga okhututa."
  74,21,"Mana naheenga."
  74,22,"Mana nakhunia obweni, nasinyikha."
  74,23,"Mana niyechesia obwatoto omukongo, mana nakhola obufuru."
  74,24,"Naboola mbu: “Bino shine shindu tawe halali obulosi bwainibwa khubandu bandi."
  74,25,"Kano shini shiosishiosi tawe halali namakhuwa kabandu sa.”"
  74,26,"Ndakhamwinjisie mumulilo omululu kwa Saqar."
  74,27,"Ne ni shina shilikhumanyia omulilo kwa Saqar oko?"
  74,28,"Shikutonyinjia inyama, ne shikulekhanga tawe."
  74,29,"Kumamulanga liselo liomubili."
  74,30,"Kulikhwo nende (Abamalaika) ekhumi nende tisa."
  74,31,"Ne shikhwakhola abalindi bomulilo halali ni Abamalaika, ne shikhwakhola isaabu yabu eyo halali okhubeyiabeyia Abakhayi, kho babe nobulaamba balia bahebwa Eshitabu, ne Abasuubila bamete obusuubili. Ne balaba nokhukanakana balia bahebwa Eshitabu nende Abasuubila tawe. Ne khobaboole balia bali nobulwale mumioyo chiabu nende Abakhayi mbu: “Nyasaye yenyanga shina, okhurulana nende okhuchelasia khuno?” Endio nilwa Nyasaye akosinjia owayenyele, nalunjisia owayenya. Ne awumao umanyile omukanda kweliyie kwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi halali Ye omwene. Ne kano shini shiosishiosi tawe halali ni ameetsulisio khubandu."
  74,32,"Tawe, nditsuba khumwesi."
  74,33,"Nende khushilo nishiwa."
  74,34,"Nende khumabwibwi olwa bushietsanga."
  74,35,"Toto omulilo oko nimulala khumakhuwa amakhongo muno."
  74,36,"Nende amekanyilisio khubandu."
  74,37,"Kho ulia wenya mwinywe, aranjilile nohomba amalilishe."
  74,38,"Buli omundu alitiilwa khulwa amakhuwa kayakhola."
  74,39,"Halali Abandu bomukhono omusatsa."
  74,40,"Baliba mumikunda chiomwikulu nibarebananga."
  74,41,"Amakhuwa ka Abandu betsimbii."
  74,42,"“Ni shina shiachila nimwinjila mumulilo kwa Saqar?”"
  74,43,"Baliboola mbu: “Efwe shikhwali mubaswaliyanga tawe."
  74,44,"Ne shikhwalisinjia abamanani tawe."
  74,45,"Ne khwali nikhweibila halala nende balia beyibila mutsimbi."
  74,46,"Ne khwali khwakatsulanga inyanga yomurungo."
  74,47,"Okhula shinga liikhuwa liatoto (lifwa) liakhuulila.”"
  74,48,"Kho okhusabila khwomusabi shikhulibakhoonya shiosishiosi tawe."
  74,49,"Mana bali barieena abahelesinjia omukongo ameetsulisio kano?"
  74,50,"Opara mbu bo nitsisishili tsisundusibwe."
  74,51,"Tsilukhanga italanyi."
  74,52,"Mbu buli omundu mubo yenyanga ahebwe eshitabu shishie okhurula mwikulu."
  74,53,"Shikali kario tawe! Halali shibaritsanga aka Mwikulu tawe."
  74,54,"Shikali kario tawe! Toto kano ni ametsulisio."
  74,55,"Kho, ulia wenya, yetsulile."
  74,56,"Ne shibakhetsulila tawe okhuula Nyasaye achame. Ye niukhoyeshele okhuribwa, khandi ni Wobulesheli muno."
